sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant API Gateway
    participant Auth Service
    participant User DB
    participant Token Store

    Browser->>API Gateway: POST /auth/login {email, password}
    API Gateway->>Auth Service: ValidateCredentials(email, password)
    Auth Service->>User DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email = ?
    User DB-->>Auth Service: user record {id, hash, roles}
    Auth Service->>Auth Service: bcrypt.verify(password, hash)

    alt credentials valid
        Auth Service->>Token Store: StoreRefreshToken(userId, token, ttl=30d)
        Token Store-->>Auth Service: stored OK
        Auth Service-->>API Gateway: {accessToken, refreshToken, expiresIn: 900}
        API Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK {accessToken, refreshToken}
    else credentials invalid
        Auth Service-->>API Gateway: 401 Unauthorized
        API Gateway-->>Browser: 401 {error: invalid_credentials}
    end

    Note over Browser,API Gateway: Subsequent authenticated request

    Browser->>API Gateway: GET /api/profile [Authorization: Bearer accessToken]
    API Gateway->>Auth Service: ValidateToken(accessToken)
    Auth Service->>Auth Service: verify JWT signature + expiry
    Auth Service-->>API Gateway: {userId, roles, valid: true}
    API Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK {profile data}

    Note over Browser,Token Store: Token refresh flow

    Browser->>API Gateway: POST /auth/refresh {refreshToken}
    API Gateway->>Token Store: LookupRefreshToken(refreshToken)
    Token Store-->>API Gateway: {userId, valid: true}
    API Gateway->>Auth Service: IssueNewTokens(userId)
    Auth Service-->>API Gateway: {newAccessToken, newRefreshToken}
    API Gateway-->>Browser: 200 OK {newAccessToken, newRefreshToken}
